=B5=CE=B9=CE=BF=CF=82 =E1=BC=80=CF=81=CE=B9=CE=B8=CE=BC=CF=8C=CF=82</span><=
/span> (<i>perfect</i>, <i>ideal</i>, or <i>complete number</i>). <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euclid" title=3D"Euclid">Euclid</a> also =
proved a formation rule (IX.36) whereby <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe=
